6w">Quá hà diệp phố - 過荷葉浦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-B%C3%AD/author-1q4TNWrg0UXqvIAXA4qwNA">Từ Bí</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BA%B1ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-M%C3%A2u/poem-lsE6nyfhf6_Cj52YBgnEjw">Tặng Đậu Mâu - 贈竇牟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BA%B1ng/author-I10VINaiadyWoHdw2FrqOQ">Dương Bằng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%A0m-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-Tam-L%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Xj0HyTmcYLTH5EbtPu2ptA">Tương Đàm điếu Tam Lư đại phu kỳ 1 - 湘潭弔三閭大夫其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/V%C4%83n-thi-%C3%B4ng-C%C3%A1t-Xuy%C3%AAn-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-thu-c%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-d%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%A1ch-trung-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ap32-i1W2hfUMoAyyDa8tw">Văn thi ông Cát Xuyên tiên sinh thu cửu nguyệt nhị thập cửu dạ khách trung ngoạ bệnh ký thị kỳ 1 - 聞詩翁葛川先生秋九月二十九夜客中臥病寄示其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br></div>	</div>
